BOLD END--> now by realistic recoil I'm not talking about counter-strike where you can hold your aim while firing several times.Im talking about you get about 1 maybe 2 clean shots on a enemy before your looking at the sky.It says in the manual &quot;Its best to aim at the enemies feet and fire until you reach there head&quot;...Yeah easier said than done.Crouching while firing is a good way to minimize the nasty kickback proning also helps a whole lot.Speeking of proning this brings me to another change.<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> 1</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->You can no longer Prone then immediately shoot.<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> 2</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->You can no longer crawl then immediately  shoot.<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> 3</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->Prone delay is still there but now it seems longer.Heck you cant even jump and shoot anymore which I don't mind to much.oh and don't get caught on a ladder...<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> FUBAR</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> yep you guessed no firing back off a ladder seems like solider boy need both hands on the ladder to climb.While still on the subject of moving theres new <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Death animations</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> A <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Sprint</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> command which sucks up you stamina faster than a triathalon.but it does have its uses you can sprint your way across a street and not worry about a sniper picking you off.Theres also new <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Hand commands</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->which you can use instead of the radio chat which the enemy can hear.A funny thing to see is someone using the hand command and waving there hands around then getting snipered.I guess it makes you more of a target.Use sparingly.The infamous <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Blood</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> which made Dod fun for me is missing.No more seeing a shot of blood fly up six feet in the air from a neck shot <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :( --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/frown.gif ALT=":("><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> ...Instead we get a very hard to see spray of blood..oh well i guess its more realistic.Speaking of looking realistic the new maps are very detailed.The explosions look and sound great.Weapons look more realistic and sound great.Theres more distinction between classes now.Sergents can now choose between the Thompson or the new M1 carbine.Theres also a new <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Class</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> to be the <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Heavy Gunner</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> 30 cal. death machines!This class puts the Heavy weapons guy from Tfc to shame.All the 30 calibers are capable of shooting 100 rounds in 5 seconds.<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Pros</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> very high rate of fire.Able to set up Tripod on sand bunkers.Shots can go thru most walls.mows down enemies in hallways<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> FUBAR</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->.<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Cons</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->Must set up Tripod to shoot accuratly.Must set up Tripod to reload.Can only set up Tripod either by proning or on certain sand bags.No secondary weapons so if you run out of ammo your...<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> FU</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->..well you get the idea.Theres a new Spawning system called <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Wave reinforcements</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->.Which basically means you spawn in waves.If someone dies they wait 8 seconds to respawn if someone does during that 8 second period they will spawn when the first guy does.Make sense?<br>
All in all they made DoD more realistic with new death animations.Stronger recoil.Detailed maps.but theres still no <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Team</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> in Team work, but there sure are a lot of <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> I's</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->.Oh well maybe next update <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :( --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/frown.gif ALT=":("><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> .<br>
